 * This function accepts two forms of attribute entries:
 *
 * default: (key, value):
 *  attrs = [key1, value1, key2, value2]
 *
 * namespaced: (NAMESPACE_MARKER, uri, name, value)
 *  attrs = [NAMESPACE_MARKER, uri, name, value, NAMESPACE_MARKER, uri, name, value]
